{"tid":1085290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃大仙男子遭3刀手狂斬 反黑接手調查","createTime":"2019-03-31T05:00:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T11:54:38.000Z","uid":122,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"35596fbe81d79439650cd21437dc60e931d01e6f","tid":1085290,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T05:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190330/large/1553951692_a9d6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190330%2Flarge%2F1553951692_a9d6.jpg&h=f09a3833&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃大仙發生斬人案，晚上近7時，一名姓黃22歲男子前往竹園南邨趣園樓停車場取車時，突然被3名持刀男子襲擊，他走避不及前臂中刀受傷，兇徒逞兇後四散，事主負傷離開及報警求助。救護員接報到場，將傷者送院治理。警方在竹雅街一垃圾桶撿獲染血手套，懷疑是兇徒遺下，案件交由反黑組接手跟進，初步不排除是黑幫尋仇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-T0zh3AmIbxo/XJTQGI3f8RI/AAAAAAAAv-Y/O7qhdWy0hHMwZ8BCZc0QHipBUl-ZSDSUgCKgBGAs/w700/1553254838_174.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-T0zh3AmIbxo%2FXJTQGI3f8RI%2FAAAAAAAAv-Y%2FO7qhdWy0hHMwZ8BCZc0QHipBUl-ZSDSUgCKgBGAs%2Fw700%2F1553254838_174.jpg&h=fcc10aa8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d71c8381048dbd2966d3737b01381d1fd39189e","tid":1085290,"uid":161731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T05:14:42.000Z","msg":"垃圾 咁都斬唔到重傷"},{"pid":"98704ba63fdaac553618b6922b9128e87d19aed7","tid":1085290,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d71c8381048dbd2966d3737b01381d1fd39189e","tid":1085290,"uid":161731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T05:14:42.000Z","msg":"垃圾 咁都斬唔到重傷"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T11:53:08.000Z","msg":"擋到"},{"pid":"ca666e9b39375e83fcad174ec3e1494885d41470","tid":1085290,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T11:54:38.000Z","msg":"我等緊佢開 你問我答 post"}]}